wiki.content: Danish 6-piece Alphabeat have already had massive success in their motherland with three hit singles and a platinum selling album. Their debut single 'Fascination' looks set to storm the charts on it's UK release in early March 2008. wiki.summary: Danish 6-piece Alphabeat have already had massive success in their motherland with three hit singles and a platinum selling album. Their debut single 'Fascination' looks set to storm the charts on it's UK release in early March 2008.
